WEBVTT
Kind: captions
Language: en

00:00:18.350 --> 00:00:20.350
Where do we begin.

00:00:21.020 --> 00:00:27.220
A year ago, these cops and lawyers wouldn't dare cross any of you. I mean, what happened ?

00:00:29.810 --> 00:00:33.610
So what are you proposing? It's simple. Kill the Batman.

00:00:40.630 --> 00:00:42.630
Here's my card.

00:00:44.000 --> 00:00:46.300
Bruce, this is Harvey Dent.

00:00:46.300 --> 00:00:47.300
Rachel's told me everything about you.

00:00:47.700 --> 00:00:49.300
Well, I certainly hope not.

00:00:51.690 --> 00:00:53.700
You once told me that we'd be together

00:00:54.000 --> 00:00:55.700
Did you mean it ?

00:00:55.700 --> 00:00:57.200
Bruce, don't make me your only hope for a normal life.

00:00:59.850 --> 00:01:01.400
You're Alfred, right ? That's right sir.

00:01:01.400 --> 00:01:03.700
Any psychotic ex-boyfriends I should be worried about ?

00:01:03.700 --> 00:01:05.700
Oh, you have no idea.

00:01:08.909 --> 00:01:10.969
Good evening, ladies and gentlemen.

00:01:13.650 --> 00:01:15.650
We are tonight's entertainment.

00:01:16.440 --> 00:01:18.440
Well hello, beautiful.

00:01:20.320 --> 00:01:22.320
You look nervous.

00:01:23.340 --> 00:01:26.600
I've seen now what I have to become to stop men like him.

00:01:28.600 --> 00:01:30.200
The night is darkest just before the dawn.

00:01:31.679 --> 00:01:33.769
I promise you, the dawn is coming.

00:01:36.329 --> 00:01:39.199
And here we go.

00:01:44.100 --> 00:01:44.700
Come on !

00:01:47.560 --> 00:01:50.560
This city deserves a better class of criminal.

00:01:52.090 --> 00:01:54.000
And I'm gonna give it to 'em.

00:01:54.000 --> 00:01:55.110
Noo !

00:01:56.860 --> 00:01:58.860
You'll see. I'll show you.

00:02:02.530 --> 00:02:07.200
You either die a hero, or you live long enough to see yourself become the villain.

00:02:18.360 --> 00:02:19.900
Will you be wanting the Batpod, sir ?

00:02:20.200 --> 00:02:21.900
In the middle of the day, Alfred ? Not very subtle.

00:02:21.900 --> 00:02:23.900
The Lamborghini, then ?

00:02:25.590 --> 00:02:27.590
Much more subtle.

